Package: pransi
Type: Package
Title: Permutation RAndom Null distributions for Simultaneous inference
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Stijn Hawinkel <stijn.hawinkel@ugent.be>
Maintainer: Joris Meys <joris.meys@ugent.be>
Description: Improves simultaneous inference under dependence of tests by
    estimating a random null distribution through permuations. Accounting for 
    the dependence between tests increases the power while reducing the
    variability of the false discovery proportion.
License: GPL-2
Encoding: UTF-8
